        "message": "LU-11930 llite: Assert on unknown flags in ll_sbi_flags_seq_show()\n\nThere really should be no valid cases for it to have any.\nEither somebody is doing development and did someting wrong,\nor we have some sort of memory corruption or other unintended\ninteractions at a client deploy where again it is not safe\nto continue anyway.\n\nChange-Id: I9403b16ac2e1835d56058af2ebfd27ca627ed75f\nSigned-off-by: Oleg Drokin <green@whamcloud.com>\n"
